comments: Williams (OKC) and Towns (MIN) engage and disengage with one another, and marginal contact occurs as they approach the screen.
Dort (OKC) engages and disengages with Towns (MIN), and marginal contact occurs prior to and as Towns sets the pick on the perimeter.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) legally contests Brown Jr.'s (MIN) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Anderson (MIN) extends slightly prior to marginal body contact occurring with Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) prior to Gilgeous-Alexander's gather.
Anderson (MIN) brings his left forearm toward Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) left leg and marginal contact occurs during Gilgeous-Alexander's driving shot attempt.
Wiggins (OKC) and Towns (MIN) engage and disengage with one another in the high post.
Holmgren (OKC) makes incidental contact with Gobert's (MIN) right arm as Gobert follows through after releasing the pass.
Williams (OKC) brushes Anderson's (MIN) front/left arm and marginal contact occurs as Anderson crosses over during the drive.
Towns (MIN) rests his hands on Wiggins' (OKC) back and marginal contact occurs as Wiggins elevates to defend the drive.
Brown Jr. (MIN) is extending into Williams' (OKC) path and does not maintain a legal guarding position prior to contact occurring after Williams' gather.
Dort (OKC) and Conley (MIN) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Williams (OKC) is established in Towns' (MIN) path prior to marginal contact occurring as they come together at the same spot in the post.

Gobert (MIN) raises his arm up and incidental contact occurs with Holmgren's (OKC) left arm prior to Gobert making contact with the part of Holmgren's hand that is on the ball, dislodging it away during the rebound.
Williams (OKC) brings his right arm forward prior to marginal contact occurring with Anderson's (MIN) slightly extended left arm as Anderson secures the rebound.
Dort (OKC) brings his right arm toward Conley's (MIN) path and marginal contact occurs with Conley's slightly extended right arm as he dribbles along the sideline.
Towns (MIN) holds both of Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) arms and initiates contact that affects Gilgeous-Alexander's ability to defend the drive.
Wiggins (OKC) maintains verticality and absorbs the incidental body contact that occurs with Brown Jr. (MIN) during the driving shot attempt.
Gobert (MIN) briefly has his arms around Holmgren's (OKC) upper half during the inbound before correcting.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) establishes himself in Brown Jr.'s (MIN) path and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the screen during the inbound.
Wiggins (OKC) moves forward toward Anderson's (MIN) space and marginal contact occurs with Anderson's front as he elevates to pass.
Williams (OKC) commits a take foul on Towns (MIN).
Anderson (MIN) slightly extends forward prior to marginal body contact occurring with Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) on the wing.
Dort (OKC) and Brown Jr. (MIN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Dort (OKC) commits a take foul on Brown Jr. (MIN).
Holmgren (OKC) momentarily has a grasp of Alexander-Walker's (MIN) left arm and then quickly releases as they each raise their arms in pursuit of the rebound.
Alexander-Walker (MIN) briefly has his arm around Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) upper half before correcting.
Brown Jr. (MIN) legally contests Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) jump shot attempt.
